text: Charles Edward Munnings (6 July 1906 – March 1995) was an English professional footballer who played in the Football League for Hull City, Mansfield Town and Swindon Town. ==References== Category:1906 births Category:1995 deaths Category:English footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:English Football League players Category:Boston Town F.C.
